{"word":"G412 - ἀνεκλάλητος - aneklálētos - an-ek-lal'-ay-tos - Unspeakable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνεκλάλητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aneklálētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ek-lal'-ay-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unspeakable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சொல்லிமுடியாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"unspeakable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G1583 - ἐκλαλέω - eklaléō - ek-lal-eh'-o/1583\">G1583</a>; <i>not spoken out</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>unutterable:</i> - unspeakable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}